                              - kind: Unknown
                                text: End
                              - kind: Whitespace
                                text: " "
                              - kind: Unknown
                                text: Function
                              - kind: Newline
                                text: "\n"
                              - kind: Newline
                                text: "\n"
                              - kind: Newline
                                text: "\n"
                              - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                text: "'The version parameter defines in which ID3v2 version the tag is written (2.3 or 2.4)."
                              - kind: Newline
                                text: "\n"
                              - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                text: "'You possibly will prefer v 2.3 because it has greater support by other programs and still"
                              - kind: Newline
                                text: "\n"
                              - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                text: "'provides all necessary functionality. For example, WinAmp only supports v 2.3."
                              - kind: Newline
                                text: "\n"
                              - kind: Newline
                                text: "\n"
                              - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                text: "'The pBuffer parameter can point to a static memory buffer which is used if the file has to"
                              - kind: Newline
                                text: "\n"
                              - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                text: "'be rewritten. The buffer should be at least as large as the file size. If no buffer is"
                              - kind: Newline
                                text: "\n"
                              - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                text: "'provided or if the buffer is too small, the memory is allocated dynamic, which is slower."
                              - kind: Newline
                                text: "\n"
                              - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                text: "'Especially when tagging more files, it's recommended to allocate a byte array of some MB and"
                              - kind: Newline
                                text: "\n"
                              - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                text: "'pass VarPtr(Buffer(0)) for the pBuffer parameter and UBound(Buffer) + 1 for the buffer size."
                              - kind: Newline
                                text: "\n"
                              - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                text: "'This is the fastest file rewriting method possible."
                              - kind: Newline
                                text: "\n"
