                                        text: "'New lines are represented by &0A& (which is chr(10)) only in ID3 v2 tags."
                                      - kind: Newline
                                        text: "\n"
                                      - kind: Whitespace
                                        text: "        "
                                      - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                        text: "'However, many programs seem to code the newline with chr(13) & chr(10),"
                                      - kind: Newline
                                        text: "\n"
                                      - kind: Whitespace
                                        text: "        "
                                      - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                        text: "'which is the windows default. Therefore, skip chr(13) and change chr(10) to vbNewLines."
